    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "O hear, the Lord is speaking: Consider now your ways,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Ye sow and bring in little, for lacking is My praise."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Go up into the mountain, material to provide,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "And build My house that I may be glorified."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Be strong, be strong, God's dwelling place to build!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "The Lord of hosts is with us, with His glory 'twill be filled!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Be strong, be strong, and work in one accord,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "That all the nations may behold the temple of the Lord."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Ye who are priests, ye remnant of Christians now obey—"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "The Lord Himself is with us, whatever men may say,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "With spirits stirred and burning, now let us come to work;"
